These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, tomato, cherry, mango
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, sunflower, poppy, amaryllis
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating pear##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growssunflower and the person who growspoppy##2
6. the person eating mango is the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Food   | mango | pear     | cherry | tomato |
| Flower     | daisy     | poppy | amaryllis  | sunflower      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, sudoku, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, disaster, animation, superhero
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Hobby   | camping | dancing    | filmmaking     | sudoku  |
| Movie-Genre     | horror    | animation | disaster | superhero |

