.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, marigold, amaryllis, lily
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, canadian, italian, thai
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
3. the italian is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the chinese is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
5. the italian is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Flower   | marigold   | amaryllis   | orchid  | lily |
| Nationality           | canadian | thai | italian | chinese  |

