.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard, helicopter, taxi
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, daisy, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who growsdaisy##2
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Transport         | skateboard | quad-bike | taxi | helicopter  |
| Flower   | marigold  | lily   | balloon-flower  | daisy |

