.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, iris, sunflower, amaryllis
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, april, may
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Flower   | balloon-flower    | iris   | sunflower | amaryllis    |
| Birthday      | august | march | april       | may |

