.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, baseball, skiing, swimming
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, go, poker
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person playing go is between the person playing poker and the person who's sport is skiing##2
3. the person playing domino is between the person playing go and the person who's sport is basketball##2
4. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Sport    | basketball | skiing | swimming | baseball |
| Game   | mah-jongg | domino  | go    | poker  |

