2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes lavender##2
5. the person playing monopoly is the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who likes lavender##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Color   | chestnut | lavender | aquamarine | mauve     |
| Game     | bridge | chess  | monopoly   | mah-jongg |

