.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, rose, aconite
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, coral, lavender, ivory
1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who growsaconite is the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Flower         | aconite | rose | daisy | begonia   |
| Color   | coral | lavender | lilac      | ivory |

