.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
City: hannover, miami, boston, marseilles
There 4 different types of food: corn, avocado, onion, grapes
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person eating corn##1
2. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
3. the person eating grapes is the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person traveling to miami is between the person eating avocado and the person eating corn##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| City     | hannover | miami   | boston      | marseilles      |
| Food   | avocado     | onion | corn | grapes |

