.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, almond-milk, coffee
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, chaman, bluemaster, bongani
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the bongani-smoker and the chaman-smoker##2
3. the person drinking sprite is the chaman-smoker##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | milk | sprite | almond-milk      | coffee   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster  | chaman    | blend | bongani |

