3. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Flower       | begonia | daisy | daffodil    | marigold      |
| Beverage   | cola       | sprite       | almond-milk | iced-tea |

