.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, horror, family, western
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cauliflower, watermelon, pumpkin
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
4. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
7. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | family  | western | horror |
| Food           | watermelon     | pumpkin | avocado    | cauliflower     |

