.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, rat, cat, mouse
City: marseilles, london, berlin, rome
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Pet   | rat  | fish | mouse  | cat      |
| City    | rome | marseilles | berlin | london |

