3. the person who's birthday is in april is the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the fish is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
6. the owner of the mouse is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday         | april | december | january | may |
| Pet   | cat     | goat       | fish   | mouse      |

