3. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes white##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Color   | orange | fuchsia | white | coral |
| Cigar         | old-henry  | bolivar   | fonseca | aristoff     |

