House: cottage, wooden, ranch-style, modern
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
4. the wooden house is on the right of the cottage house##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Sport      | soccer | rowing    | baseball  | water-polo |
| House   | cottage       | wooden | ranch-style | modern  |

