2. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
3. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Color   | black        | ebony       | chestnut   | emerald |
| Music-Genre    | folk | reggae | blues | r&b  |

