.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, martial-arts, documentary, drama
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, azalea, daffodil, begonia
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
4. the person who growstulip is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
6. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | disaster     | documentary          | drama |
| Flower      | tulip | azalea | begonia | daffodil  |

 